name: LRM - Liangyiu's Realistic Mix
description:
Liang's Realistic Mix

This merge is my first attempt and I am pretty happy with how it turned out, so I wanted to share it.

It's a mega-merge by someone who has no idea what he is doing :D

Settings/Workflow

The model responds well when prompted for photorealism and prompts in that direction, e.g. ((photorealistic):1.1), (raw, 8k:1.2), (textured skin, skin pores:1.2), (moles:0.8), (imperfect skin:1.1), intricate details

  • Sampler: UniPC, Heun, DPM2 a

  • Steps: 30~50

  • Width: 512px

  • Height: 768px

  • CFG Scale: 3~7

  • (optional) ADetailer for faces

VAE

This model comes baked with the vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.safetensors VAE.

Credits & Merge Parameters

  • GalaxyTimeMachine's GTM "ForYou-Photo" v1.1 - Base

  • cineMaErosPG_V4 - Strength 0.2

  • Am i Real v3 - Strength 0.2

  • ICBINP - "I Can't Believe It's Not Photography" v8 - Strength 0.2

  • CyberRealistic v3 - Strength 0.1

  • HyperV1 ClipFixed - Strength 0.1

  • Noise Offset for True Darkness in SD - Strength 0.2

  • epi_noiseoffset v2 - Strength 0.3

Added to create the fixed version:

  • Deliberate v2 - Strength 0.2

  • Consistent-Factor v4 Vivid - Strength 0.3

  • Lyriel v1.5 - Strength 0.4

  • Analog Madness - Realistic model v4 - Strength 0.3

  • Clarity v2 - Strength 0.2

  • Babes v2 - Strength 0.4

  • QGO PromptingReal v1 - Strength 0.3

  • Ares Mix v0.2 - Strength 0.2

  • Avalon TRUvision v3.1 - Strength 0.15

  • A-Zovya Photoreal v1 - Strength 0.25

  • and some more contrast

v1.1 adds:

  • AbsoluteReality v1 - Base

  • ReV Animated v1.2.2 - Strength 0.15

  • RunDiffusion FX Photorealistic v1 - Strength 0.2

  • ICBINP - "I Can't Believe It's Not Photography" final - Strength 0.3

  • Juggernaut v1.9 - Strength 0.3

  • CyberRealistic Classic v1.2 - Strength 0.2

  • PurePerfection v2 - Strength 0.2

  • Noise Offset for True Darkness in SD v1 - Strength 0.25

The above have then been merged with v1_fixed (0.6).
